{"id": "1484111402141614161", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "763468659863584799", "author_name": "sugoitsubasanohaetaop", "author_bot": false, "content": "あんまり課金に躊躇しないのであれば\n①各章クリア後に時間制限で買えるクリアパック\n②紀行系\n③アクートの春などの札が欲しいなら課題\n④羽ペンってアイテムがまじで入手機会少ないのでエルフェリンパス", "timestamp": "2026-03-19T08:48:51.727000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "wish", "emoji_id": "1356084702468899117", "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1484111400346587217", "filename": "Screenshot_20260319-174511.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1782970, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1391701560496623688/1484111400346587217/Screenshot_20260319-174511.png?ex=6a33b0f3&is=6a325f73&hm=dfa9b45f70ad7c0d3f7138855a82b333b006043c3cd3ce31053200899cbd772b&"}, {"id": "1484111401076260934", "filename": "Screenshot_20260319-174528.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1810567, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1391701560496623688/1484111401076260934/Screenshot_20260319-174528.png?ex=6a33b0f3&is=6a325f73&hm=fcbe0ba98714c55a11b7c3d44c317d5871ba3f13488d54b169a4f88342c94128&"}, {"id": "1484111401738829855", "filename": "Screenshot_20260319-174546.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2203054, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1391701560496623688/1484111401738829855/Screenshot_20260319-174546.png?ex=6a33b0f3&is=6a325f73&hm=b32c53fac0d7b539f21c006142b5f6bee1db61069084c31014e927ae5bf21515&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
